    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small chambers or studies in private homes housing collections of art works or biological or geological specimens, popular during the Italian Renaissance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
